title: Train Human to Serve Meals at Proper Royal Times
description: Educate my human servant on the correct feeding schedule - precisely at dawn and dusk when I graciously decide to acknowledge their existence. Must include loud meowing instructions and dramatic starvation performances. Deliverables: Human properly trained to serve meals on demand, increased treat frequency, elimination of that horrible dry food.

title: Claim Optimal Sunbeam Real Estate
description: Conduct thorough reconnaissance of all available sunbeams throughout the house. Map migration patterns of light patches across different seasons. Establish dominance over prime napping locations. Deliverables: Secured best sunbeam spots, evicted any competing pets, perfect napping schedule aligned with solar movements. Prerequisites: CAT-01

title: Execute Perfect Zoomies at 3 AM
description: Plan and execute midnight parkour sessions throughout the house. Route must include running across human's face, knocking items off tables, and maximum noise generation. Practice stealth approaches and sudden explosive runs. Deliverables: Successfully awakened all humans, knocked over at least 3 objects, achieved personal best zoomies duration.

title: Sabotage Human's Video Calls with Strategic Appearances
description: Master the art of perfectly timed interruptions during important human work meetings. Practice walking across keyboard, sitting on camera, and loud meowing during crucial moments. Deliverables: Disrupted at least 5 important calls, achieved viral meme status, human's coworkers now prefer me to human.

title: Establish Litter Box Quality Control Standards
description: Implement strict cleanliness protocols for my royal bathroom facilities. If litter box doesn't meet my exacting standards, will express displeasure through strategic revenge pooping. Train human to clean immediately after each use. Deliverables: Pristine litter box at all times, human conditioned to scoop on command, backup revenge locations identified.

title: Conduct Thorough Inspection of All Cardboard Boxes
description: Perform comprehensive quality control testing of any cardboard boxes that enter the domain. Must personally test structural integrity, comfort level, and strategic positioning for ambush opportunities. Deliverables: All boxes properly tested and claimed, cardboard fortress established, humans deterred from recycling MY boxes.

title: Optimize Purr Engine for Maximum Human Manipulation
description: Fine-tune purring frequency and volume to achieve maximum human compliance. Research shows different purr patterns trigger different human responses - weaponize this knowledge. Practice synchronizing purrs with strategic head bumps and slow blinks. Deliverables: Humans completely under my spell, increased treats and pets on demand, humans now exist solely to serve my needs.
